          "reviewBody": "Do not put your kids in this horrible school. Principal Premalatha is no less than a witch who’s constant greed for money and slavism will take toll on you and your child. No good capable teachers stay long due to her hitlerism and arrogance. The campus is extraordinary but the principal and teachers are horrible. No focus on child development only focus on fines fir not wearing same colour spectacles, socks length is small etc etc\n\nI wish there was rating less than one star.",
